Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:15.01,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\blur1\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:15.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:19.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:23.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:26.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:30.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:33.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:40.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:44.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:48.40,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:51.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:54.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:59.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:02.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.83,0:01:25.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mexico, part of the\NNorth American continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:29.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Palas River, host to the Palas\NDam, runs through its center.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.22,0:01:33.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The power this dam provides is an\Nimportant artery of the Mexican economy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:55.29,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,210.389)}The Devilish Sabotegron
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:55.29,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(367.167,520.389)}Attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The destruction of the dam has\Nthrown all of Mexico into chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.95,0:02:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker will take advantage of\Nthat chaos to conquer Mexico City.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.97,0:02:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabotegron.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The destructive activities of Shocker's\NMexico Branch are close to complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there is much more to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Our plans to conquer\NMexico are 90% complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabotegron.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to put your spectacular\Nleadership to use in another region.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What region is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You must fly to Japan, where Shocker's\Nplans have been lagging behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting. As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finally get to meet this Kamen\NRider who's been giving our commanders
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so much trouble, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight the Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then destroy all of Japan's dams,\Nand throw the country into chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A message from the FBI's special\Ninvestigations department.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"A member of Shocker's Mexican\Ncommand team is heading for Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be arriving on\NFlight 603 in Haneda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Reference attached file six."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Flight 603 into Haneda, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I won't make it to the\Nopening of the Tachibana Racing Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.53,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\an7\fs60\c&H000000&\3c&HDBE6DC&}To Taki Kazuya
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:47.54,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs60\c&H85464C&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Tachibana Auto Corner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry we're late.\NI'll make some introductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Michi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We're joining the club. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro, stop gaping and\Nshow some hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.51,0:04:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a seat in the back, everyone.\NRight this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's so groovy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Any experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a little\Nexperience with a 90cc.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a first-degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A first-degree\Nblackbelt in karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I do fencing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what\NI'm asking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.73,0:04:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean motorbike experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,None at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,None at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we need\Nlessons already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:01.14,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\c&H3249C3&}International Arrivals
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be out\Nof customs by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the message from HQ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about a Shocker\Ncommander from Mexico?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's a tricky one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He shook off our attempts to tail him,\Nbut we've managed to locate him in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll join you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops! Don't be a fuddy-duddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some fun with\Nthe young people!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna dance, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold this, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids these days, I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, Taki...\Nthey're just as bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:14.73,Sign,,0,0,0,,Autopilot Remote Control
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on. Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:27.87,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,The fact that it started up on its\Nown means Hongo's calling it remotely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:33.78,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,I can sleep all the way to Hongo,\Nas long as I stay on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:45.04,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I like this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:49.02,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,And it's not good to take\Nsomeone completely at face value.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We have some news to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A body was found\Naboard Flight 603
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:08:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,from Mexico City arriving at\NHaneda at 2:00 this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The body belonged\Nto an FBI agent...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you turn it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Mexican\NShocker commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,FBI scum...\Nyour comrade is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All who oppose Shocker must\Nbe wiped from the planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one\Nwho's going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mistake was putting\Nme behind the wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops! You came to save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Shocker monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not safe here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make tracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, combatants of\NShocker's Japan Branch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Prove yourselves to\Nthe great Sabotegron!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll crush all three\Nof you at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.88,0:11:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Be gentle, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You left your customers\Nbehind to go off on a drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hurting, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be such a\Nbaby, married man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What, he's married?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What a rotten trick.\NGo do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There, all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But where's Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that sounds like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone, hide! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.59,0:11:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro, turn off the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro, turn on the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of a welcome is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? I'm Ichimonji Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a freelance photographer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And what exactly do\Nyou want with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot something,\Nthat's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgot something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your motorbike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please!\NPhotograph me, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I don't do women.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:55.79,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:12:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabotegron.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The combatants of Shocker's Japan\NBranch are yours to command.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Embark upon wide-scale\Ndestruction at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Members of the Japan Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we embark upon\Nour reign of destruction,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to show you an\Nexperiment using the cactus bombs,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,also known as the Mexican Flowers,\Nwhich I perfected back in Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They look exactly\Nlike regular cacti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But the spikes on the cactus\Nare extremely sensitive fuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything they contact will\Nbe destroyed without a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That is how Mexican Flowers die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, you'll all be able to see the\Npower of these bombs with your own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:14:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Our guinea pigs will be any humans foolish\Nenough to try to learn Shocker's secrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taki. Slow down already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I said you could sit this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I know you're going\Nout to find Shocker's base,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't come along,\NI could never show my face again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be sure that their base\Nreally is in these mountains, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not nice to strike at\Nsomeone the moment you see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you following us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:14:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I\Nwas following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was walking ahead of\Nyou, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that explains that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fall for his nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.95,0:15:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're with Shocker, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more about shutters, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.09,0:15:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shutters?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't get a straight\Nanswer from this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not even\Ngoing the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you'd better not follow\Nus, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Unusual to see this\Ncactus species here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It originates in\NMexico, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it doing in\Na place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All that fuss for\Na stupid cactus...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, we're wasting time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignorance is bliss, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.74,0:16:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought...\Nwe've finally found Shocker's base!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we're here,\Nwe don't really have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... we fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,After nightfall, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That amateur can't handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I'm coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,These cacti are bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you touch their\Nthorns, they blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Bombs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.67,0:17:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you think I'm lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare a man like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mexican Flowers\Ndon't bloom so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll only let them bloom\Nonce I use my decoys
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to lure out Shocker's true\Nenemy, the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we might have\Nwalked into a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better beat it, fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good.\NWe'd better leave for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... they've herded us\Ninto a field of cactus bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the frying pan,\Ninto the fire, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Shocker's true target...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy to Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And friend to humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi left Japan to\Nstop a different Shocker scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What, he's in another country?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Ruriko went with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruriko, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I protect Japan in\NHongo Takeshi's place...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're also a cyborg?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to demonstrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is... the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bloom, Mexican Flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.21,0:22:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.37,0:22:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.38,0:23:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.04,0:23:32.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider is in peril!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:36.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will he be struck down by\Nthat Shocker devil, Sabotegron?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:40.96,Cont,,490,0,160,,{\blur.8\fad(0,440)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:43.76,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(502.031,486.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:46.80,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fscx100\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(512.419,299.405)}Sabotegron Strikes Back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:44.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.68,0:23:46.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the devilish Sabotegron.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.18,0:23:49.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The devilish Sabotegron,\Ndispatched from Shocker's Mexican Branch,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.60,0:23:53.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,uses cactus bombs known as Mexican Flowers\Nto drive Kamen Rider to desperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.96,0:23:56.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A deathmatch unfolds in\Na field thick with cacti.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.83,0:24:01.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for\N"Sabotegron Strikes Back!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:10.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.43,0:24:13.43,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.43,0:24:15.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.39,0:24:18.43,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.93,0:24:20.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.81,0:24:22.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.69,0:24:24.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.48,0:24:25.82,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.27,0:24:28.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.36,0:24:34.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.03,0:24:37.62,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.62,0:24:41.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.71,0:24:45.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!